title: Request to generate blacklist files for other genomes
body: Hello, I work with rice (Oryza sativa). Can you please provide the blacklisted regions for the [rice genome](http://rice.uga.edu/pub/data/Eukaryotic_Projects/o_sativa/annotation_dbs/pseudomolecules/version_7.0/all.dir/) to be used in ChIP-seq analyses?
